{
  "stem": "9665.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And some also here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we were not asleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We were afraid that they're going to rob us, because without money, it was very, very difficult to get through.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then they picked us up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So we were in what you called France Libre, unoccupied France.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we didn't realize that unoccupied France was worse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "You know, Vichy France was worse than occupied France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But we are coming to that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We were brought to a place called [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we were put up in a hotel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We had to go to the police, to the [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we were told that we have to go to-- again with the Eislands, that we will have to go to a [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "That is, they had some [FRENCH] places where the refugees were put up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I did not want to go there, fortunately.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because all the people of the [FRENCH] within a few months, they were put in the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these were the first one, even before the Dutch, before the people in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are put in a train to Poland, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I forgot to tell you that my sister, Anna Feigenbaum from Antwerp and her husband, and Paulette, when the Germans came to Belgium, they escaped like so many hundreds of thousands to France.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were in Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister wired this [NON-ENGLISH], we should get out, which we knew ourselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we should know what we are doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so the first thing, I did in the hotel, [INAUDIBLE] my sister in Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She couldn't travel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
